    87→the model’s internal algorithm misreads one of the
    88→digits in the input. We show this rigorously in §2.
    89→We argue that such scattered error distributions
    90→are unlikely to occur in models that directly ma-
    91→nipulate numbers in a value space. For example,
    92→in multi-operand addition, if the model represents
