  1109→A.3
  1110→Accuracy of circular probes
  1111→In the main results we showed the accuracy of the
  1112→circular digit-wise probes, averaged over layers
  1113→≥3. Here we will show this choice is justified
  1114→as can be seen in Figure 7. While there is signifi-
