   183→where Win and Wout are learned parameters, and S injects an inductive bias in the classifier towards
   184→sinusoidal representations. We build upon an assumption verified by Kadlˇc´ık et al. (2025) stating
   185→that sinusoidal probes indeed adapt and employ a sinusoidal representation from inductive bias, if a
   186→sinusoidal representation is also present in the input embeddings.
   187→We first assess whether sinusoidal probes are the most suitable, i.e., an accurate choice for decoding
